Package com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.sha

Class ShaFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.sha.ShaFactory
  • public class ShaFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    ShaFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.sha package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
